                        Special Features
                        
   o Pyedit runs wherever pyGTK is available.
   o Fast enough for large files
   o Easily customizable
   o Macro Record / Play 
   o Comfortable key presets for Linux / Windows / Mac users
   o Multi window Editing
   o Regex and multi search / replace
   o UI remembers last settings, last files
   o Interactive status bar to let you know what is happening
   o Spell check, code spell check
   o Syntax coloring (primitive coloring for speed)
   o Configurable
   o easy to extend, it is written in python
   o Undo / Redo that survives 
   
   o Lots lots more ...
                          
                          
 


